{"tid":1092734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：公民黨慶Tanya判刑前唱《夢伴》 「剩下我北風中漆黑中帶着淚」 - 李八方","createTime":"2019-04-05T05:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T07:16:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ead250bb6ed8c543556a2d2740ceab334296d81","tid":1092734,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190405/20649588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190405%2F20649588&d=Ibp2r5avkWIk14HZtW%2BzJ%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=d2cdb05f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190405%2F20649588&h=852c3375\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190405/20649588</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：公民黨慶Tanya判刑前唱《夢伴》<br />\n「剩下我北風中漆黑中帶着淚」 - 李八方<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190405/large/a1304a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190405%2Flarge%2Fa1304a.gif&h=6e4ac8cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下周面對佔中案判刑嘅陳淑莊，一曲《夢伴》帶起全場氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n公民黨13歲生日，噚日喺金鐘名都酒樓以「並肩向前」為主題開party，事前講明唔請官員，但現場政商界雲集，仍然星光熠熠，民主派友好固然現身，建制派「班長」廖長江、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀、自由黨榮譽主席田北俊等都有到場，屢被公民黨狙擊嘅港鐵都派出車務總監劉天成、英美澳加領事都有畀面出席，不過講到全晚最耀眼嘅，相信係下星期面對佔中案判刑嘅陳淑莊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190405/large/a1304c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190405%2Flarge%2Fa1304c.gif&h=2c6fcfb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190405/large/05ls5p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190405%2Flarge%2F05ls5p05.jpg&h=659ee15f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190405/large/a1304b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190405%2Flarge%2Fa1304b.gif&h=e0c5cf2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公民黨13周年黨慶，講明唔請官員，但現場一樣星光熠熠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳副領事︰睇《蘋果》學中文<br />\n<br />\nTanya唱歌一向有水準，佢噚晚為黨慶唱咗梅艷芳嘅《夢伴》，仲有陳百強嘅《深愛着你》幫公民黨籌款，Tanya唱得好聽唔在講，仲炒熱全場氣氛，全場為佢歡呼，雖然Tanya早走，不過八方相信今天星閃閃，唔會剩低Tanya一人漆黑中帶北風中帶着淚。除咗Tanya唱歌，黨主席梁家傑都獻唱一首《My Way》，前執委余若薇除咗拍賣墨寶，仲拎自家設計兼製作嘅小朋友衫，限量五件拍賣，每件盛惠3,888元。最後全晚共籌到285萬。<br />\n<br />\n因為《逃犯條例》修訂，令在場嘅各國領事都成為焦點，雖然各領事唔願多作評論，但都好樂意同傳媒傾偈，話晒喺香港工作，都有展示一下廣東話水平，澳洲駐香港總領事館副領事（政治/經濟）Suzanne Passmore廣東話講得唔錯，仲識睇中文，佢同八方講平時睇《蘋果》新聞學中文，連短片都有睇，話可以學到地道字句喎。<br />\n<br />\n李八方  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n江湖滾熱辣 (馬龍)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：「問候689」籌款爆額 吳文遠︰梁實在太乞人憎 (李八方)"},{"pid":"8f6bb92e151a18cacd09f73267f5e024c9c26658","tid":1092734,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"你係夢伴裏面條蚯蚓咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1665e22356128b6adaa83c19f34d8d85d24773c","tid":1092734,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T07:16:05.000Z","msg":"識唱一齊唱"}]}